    {
      "text": "Become a master of this mysterious ancient art; progress from novice to Tenth Dan and test your strength and discipline. 18 different manoeuvres including blocks, flying kicks, leg sweeps, roundhouse and even somersaults! Unreleased until leaked in 2012.\nIt was later released in cartridge by Piko Interactive in 2019.",
